def create_team(
    data: TeamCreate,
    user: Annotated[User, Depends(get_current_user)],
    session: Annotated[Session, Depends(get_session)],
):
    team = Team(name=data.name, user_id=user.id)
    session.add(team)
    session.commit()
    session.refresh(team)
    return team
